short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Redirects you from reddit.com to lemmy.world

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: This extension is designed to assist users who are transitioning from Reddit.com to Lemmy.world but still have a habit of visiting Reddit out of muscle memory. It helps redirect users from Reddit.com to Lemmy.world, allowing them to easily shift their online browsing experience. Say goodbye to unintentional visits to Reddit and embrace a new community on lemmy.world with this helpful Chrome extension
